CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. 14 reads: "Visiting Pittsburgh to take part in ABA tournament were some gorgeous gals and handsome men. Here, left to right,...Mrs. Janice Wilkins, Detroit..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of two women, including Janice Wilkins on left, posed in Fort Pitt Hotel for 24th annual American Bridge Association tournament
